data.text:
We work with Universities and Great Companies around the world, Whether for data analytics, marketing, AI, economics or business we are pleased to offer our knowledge, insights and hands-on experience into whatever direction technology is taking you, Together with innovations worthy of note we offer background and context on how to improve and perfect current practices and techniques involved around ecommerce.

Our core speciality is AI hyper-personalisation, using all the data captured when a consumer uses an ecommerce website. Compliant with each respective countrys international AI, Data Security and Privacy legislation, and strictly with each consumers permission. It is used to perfect the interaction between that individual and the products each retailer offers, for mutual benefit. Our investment in this technology is to pioneer the science into the acknowledgement and appreciation of the individual.

We are delighted to welcome both chancellery, administration and students alike from many of the greatest Universities, Colleges and Schools of higher education around the world. Whether our content contributes to course-work, research or is part of your syllabus, we are happy to oblige.
